{"tid":637812,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Pixel 2 cast 搵唔到 device","createTime":"2018-04-22T07:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T10:01:52.000Z","uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fca92ea7a3c58466ab4222ae3e8dc17111fb8a","tid":637812,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"屋企用Hisense smart TV，內置Android 系統同cast receiver<br />\n<br />\n之前用小米3手機(rooted)，可以cast上電視。電視介面有個選項『斷開(電視的)Wifi連接並啟動鏡像』，跟住手機個cast就會search 到電視。cast連接後，成部手機聲畫上哂電視，不限於某個app或者播某段片<br />\n<br />\n(上網睇，呢種應該叫miracast?)<br />\n<br />\n換左Pixel 2之後，佢個cast 就冇再搵到電視<br />\n<br />\n岩岩落去電腦商場，有啲叫xxcast 嘅手指可以插去電視，應該比非smart TV用。我諗可能可以代替電視內置嘅cast receiver，或者同Pixel 2 夾得來。<br />\n<br />\n我試左easy cast(個連接方法唔同，要隻easy cast手指開Wifi hotspot, 再用手機連個hotspot Wifi，再喺手機cast 介面搵device)，但Pixel 2都係搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多其他款，包括Google親生嘅chrome cast，但冇得試，算了<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過，似乎都有其他人有pixel 2搵唔到cast device 嘅問題，仲要Chromecast 都會搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位師兄，有冇人知道可以點搞？有冇邊隻cast 手指確定可以駁到pixel 2？"},{"pid":"f5d09308085880975681bafdd3ec28161801c462","tid":637812,"uid":41927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pixel 2要用番 Google Chromecast （除非root機）, 我都係Pixel 2 XL 用家，最近先知。"},{"pid":"51e84d0417692f9d5cdbc4002b7c29b7bd0ee7d7","tid":637812,"uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f5d09308085880975681bafdd3ec28161801c462","tid":637812,"uid":41927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pixel 2要用番 Google Chromecast （除非root機）, 我都係Pixel 2 XL 用家，最近先知。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcc3827c304e866dbb949f69b925131a500608f","tid":637812,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d09308085880975681bafdd3ec28161801c462","tid":637812,"uid":41927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"Pixel 2要用番 Google Chromecast （除非root機）, 我都係Pixel 2 XL 用家，最近先知。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T23:23:14.000Z","msg":"多謝Ching，或者我買來搏下<br />\n<br />\n之前上網睇有人話連chrome cast 都連接唔到，所以唔敢搏"},{"pid":"892fde4f4a1236e57a7fd4cdfd1b2296688c7745","tid":637812,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"Google 想迫你買多舊 chromecast 賺多你一舊錢<br />\n自從 update 咗某一代 Android 開始佢就 lock 咗 Miracast<br />\n硬件其實 support <br />\n係 Google 特登 lock 你<br />\n<br />\n之前用 Miracast 可以用 Terrarium TV cast 上電視收 Netflix 皮<br />\n依家唔得"},{"pid":"076d17c98bec05642394fd61486c3b328cae1ff3","tid":637812,"uid":37916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"892fde4f4a1236e57a7fd4cdfd1b2296688c7745","tid":637812,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"Google 想迫你買多舊 chromecast 賺多你一舊錢<br />\n自從 update 咗某一代 Android 開始佢就 lock 咗 Miracast<br />\n硬件其實 support <br />\n係 Google 特登 lock 你<br />\n<br />\n之前用 Miracast 可以用 Terrarium TV cast 上電視收 Netflix 皮<br />\n依家唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"大部分正版影視<br />\n例如google play同netflix都唔想你用miracast<br />\n因為冇防盜錄（hdcp）<br />\n唔可以怪曬google"},{"pid":"f2248c0fc67f9611531098ff7c5ef61c44ce391e","tid":637812,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076d17c98bec05642394fd61486c3b328cae1ff3","tid":637812,"uid":37916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"892fde4f4a1236e57a7fd4cdfd1b2296688c7745","tid":637812,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"Google 想迫你買多舊 chromecast 賺多你一舊錢<br />\n自從 update 咗某一代 Android 開始佢就 lock 咗 Miracast<br />\n硬件其實 support <br />\n係 Google 特登 lock 你<br />\n<br />\n之前用 Miracast 可以用 Terrarium TV cast 上電視收 Netflix 皮<br />\n依家唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"大部分正版影視<br />\n例如google play同netflix都唔想你用miracast<br />\n因為冇防盜錄（hdcp）<br />\n唔可以怪曬google"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-